data.description: Welcome to this  All Brick Single Story Home located in the Desirable Kings Grant of Summerville! This Lovely 3 Bedroom 2 Bath with Beautiful Vaulted Ceiling welcoming Natural Daylight in the Livingroom will be Great for your Family and Entertaining.  The Family room has a Wood Burning Fireplace for the Cozy Nights. Enjoy the Holidays eating in the Formal Dining Room. Updated Windows throughout. The Frog (not included in sq. ft.) has Endless Possibilities.  Game room, Art Studio, Office. You decide!!  This Property Won't Last!!
